<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="site-title">
            <img src="/icon.png" alt="Awing Logo" class="header-logo">
            <span>AWING HERITAGE</span>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/" class="active">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/origin">Origins</a></li>
                <li><a href="/meals">Meals</a></li>
                <li><a href="/customs">Customs</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>The Awing Kingdom</h1>
        <p>Welcome to one of the most vibrant traditional communities of the North-West Region of Cameroon. Explore our rich heritage preserved through generations.</p>
    </section>

    <h2 style="text-align: center; font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: #8B4513; margin-top: 40px; font-size: 2rem;">Discover Our Culture</h2>
    
    <div class="container">
        
        <a href="/origin" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
            <div class="carte portal-card">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <span class="tag">History</span>
                    <h2>Origins & Lineage</h2>
                    <p>Trace the Tikar roots of the Awing people, the history of our fondom, and the mysteries surrounding the Sacred Lake.</p>
                    <span class="read-more">Explore &rarr;</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/meals" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
            <div class="carte portal-card">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <span class="tag">Gastronomy</span>
                    <h2>Royal Culinary Arts</h2>
                    <p>Delve into the famous Achuh yellow soup, the staples of our soil, and the ancestral etiquette of eating in the kingdom.</p>
                    <span class="read-more">Explore &rarr;</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/customs" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
            <div class="carte portal-card">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <span class="tag">Traditions</span>
                    <h2>Customs & Ceremonies</h2>
                    <p>Understand the traditional marriage rites, the power of secret societies like the Nchinda, and the rhythms of the Keleng dance.</p>
                    <span class="read-more">Explore &rarr;</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>

    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Awing Cultural Project - All Rights Reserved</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>